### ========================================
### 6.2.1 用户管理模块测试
### ========================================

### TC-REG-001: 正常注册USER角色
POST http://localhost:8080/api/user/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "testuser001",
  "password": "123456",
  "realName": "张三",
  "phone": "13800138001"
}

### TC-REG-002: 用户名重复注册(应返回400)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/user/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "testuser001",
  "password": "123456",
  "realName": "李四",
  "phone": "13800138002"
}

### TC-REG-003: 手机号格式错误(应返回400)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/user/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "testuser002",
  "password": "123456",
  "realName": "王五",
  "phone": "02345678901"
}

### TC-REG-004: 手机号为空(应成功)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/user/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "testuser003",
  "password": "123456",
  "realName": "赵六",
  "phone": ""
}

### TC-REG-005: 密码为空(应返回500)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/user/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "testuser004",
  "password": "",
  "realName": "孙七",
  "phone": "13800138004"
}

### TC-LOG-001: 正常登录(USER角色)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/user/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "testuser001",
  "password": "123456"
}

### TC-LOG-002: 用户名不存在(应返回401)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/user/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "nonexistent",
  "password": "123456"
}

### TC-LOG-003: 密码错误(应返回401)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/user/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "testuser001",
  "password": "wrongpassword"
}

### TC-PROF-001: 修改头像和简介
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/user/update-profile
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "testuser001",
  "avatar": "/uploads/avatar.jpg",
  "bio": "这是我的简介"
}

### TC-PROF-002: 修改密码(原密码正确)
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/user/update-profile
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "testuser001",
  "oldPassword": "123456",
  "newPassword": "654321"
}

### TC-PROF-003: 修改密码(原密码错误,应返回401)
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/user/update-profile
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "testuser001",
  "oldPassword": "wrong",
  "newPassword": "654321"
}

### TC-PROF-004: 新密码长度不足6位(应返回400)
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/user/update-profile
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "testuser001",
  "oldPassword": "654321",
  "newPassword": "123"
}

### ========================================
### 6.2.2 宠物管理模块测试
### ========================================

### TC-PET-001: 正常发布宠物
POST http://localhost:8080/api/pet/publish
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "小橘",
  "type": "猫",
  "gender": "母",
  "age": 2,
  "description": "性格温顺",
  "username": "testuser001"
}

### TC-PET-002: 发布宠物(含图片URL)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/pet/publish
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "小黑",
  "type": "狗",
  "gender": "公",
  "age": 3,
  "description": "活泼可爱",
  "photoUrl": "http://example.com/dog.jpg",
  "username": "testuser001"
}

### TC-PET-003: 发布宠物(含健康状态)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/pet/publish
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "小白",
  "type": "猫",
  "gender": "母",
  "age": 1,
  "description": "已疫苗已绝育",
  "isVaccinated": true,
  "isNeutered": true,
  "isDewormed": false,
  "username": "testuser001"
}

### TC-PET-004: 宠物名称为空(应返回400)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/pet/publish
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "",
  "type": "猫",
  "description": "测试",
  "username": "testuser001"
}

### TC-PET-005: 宠物种类为空(应返回400)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/pet/publish
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "小橘",
  "type": "",
  "description": "测试",
  "username": "testuser001"
}

### TC-PET-006: 用户不存在(应返回400)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/pet/publish
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "小橘",
  "type": "猫",
  "description": "测试",
  "username": "nonexistent"
}

### TC-PET-007: 年龄字段为字符串
POST http://localhost:8080/api/pet/publish
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "小黄",
  "type": "狗",
  "gender": "公",
  "age": "3",
  "description": "测试",
  "username": "testuser001"
}

### TC-PET-008: 年龄字段缺失(应使用默认值1)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/pet/publish
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "小小",
  "type": "猫",
  "gender": "母",
  "description": "测试",
  "username": "testuser001"
}

### 查询刚发布的宠物ID(假设ID为1,实际使用时替换为真实ID)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/pet/1

### TC-EDIT-001: 发布者正常编辑
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/pet/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "testuser001",
  "name": "小橘(已编辑)"
}

### TC-EDIT-002: 非发布者尝试编辑(应返回400)
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/pet/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "testuser002",
  "name": "被篡改的名字"
}

### TC-EDIT-003: 编辑不存在的宠物(应返回400)
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/pet/99999
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "testuser001",
  "name": "测试"
}

### TC-DEL-001: 发布者删除宠物
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/pet/1?username=testuser001

### ========================================
### 6.2.3 领养申请模块测试
### ========================================

### 先发布一个宠物用于测试领养申请
POST http://localhost:8080/api/pet/publish
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "待领养宠物",
  "type": "猫",
  "gender": "母",
  "age": 2,
  "description": "等待领养",
  "username": "testuser001"
}

### 注册一个领养者
POST http://localhost:8080/api/user/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "adopter001",
  "password": "123456",
  "realName": "领养者",
  "phone": "13800138010"
}

### TC-APP-001: 正常提交申请(假设宠物ID为2)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/adoption/apply
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "petId": 2,
  "username": "adopter001",
  "reason": "非常喜欢这只猫",
  "contact": "13800138002",
  "residenceType": "自有住房",
  "housingArea": 80,
  "petExperience": "养过2年猫",
  "hasOtherPets": false,
  "otherPetsInfo": ""
}

### TC-APP-002: 对已被领养的宠物提交申请(需先手动将宠物状态改为ADOPTED)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/adoption/apply
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "petId": 999,
  "username": "adopter001",
  "reason": "测试",
  "contact": "13800138002"
}

### TC-APP-003: 宠物不存在(应返回400)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/adoption/apply
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "petId": 99999,
  "username": "adopter001",
  "reason": "测试",
  "contact": "13800138002"
}

### TC-APP-004: 用户不存在(应返回400)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/adoption/apply
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "petId": 2,
  "username": "nonexistent",
  "reason": "测试",
  "contact": "13800138002"
}

### 注册管理员用于审核
POST http://localhost:8080/api/user/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin001",
  "password": "admin123",
  "realName": "管理员",
  "phone": "13800138999"
}

### 查询待审核申请列表
GET http://localhost:8080/api/adoption/pending?username=admin001&page=0&size=10

### TC-REVAPP-001: 管理员通过第一个申请(假设申请ID为1)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/adoption/review/1?username=admin001&action=approve

### TC-REVAPP-002: 管理员尝试通过第二个申请(并发冲突,应返回400)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/adoption/review/2?username=admin001&action=approve

### TC-REVAPP-003: 管理员拒绝申请
POST http://localhost:8080/api/adoption/review/3?username=admin001&action=reject&reason=住房面积太小

### TC-REVAPP-004: 重复审核已通过申请(应返回400)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/adoption/review/1?username=admin001&action=approve

### TC-REVAPP-005: 无效的操作参数(应返回400)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/adoption/review/1?username=admin001&action=invalid

