### 6.2.4 互助社区模块测试
### ========================================

### TC-POST-001: 正常发布帖子
POST http://localhost:8080/api/help/publish
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "寻找丢失的猫咪",
  "content": "详细描述...",
  "category": "寻宠启事",
  "username": "testuser001"
}

### TC-POST-002: 发布带城市的帖子
POST http://localhost:8080/api/help/publish
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "北京流浪猫救助",
  "content": "详细描述...",
  "category": "救助信息",
  "city": "北京",
  "username": "testuser001"
}

### TC-POST-003: 发布关联宠物的帖子(假设宠物ID为1)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/help/publish
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "小橘的成长日记",
  "content": "详细描述...",
  "category": "经验分享",
  "relatedPetId": 1,
  "username": "testuser001"
}

### TC-POST-004: 标题为空(应返回400)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/help/publish
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "",
  "content": "测试",
  "category": "经验分享",
  "username": "testuser001"
}

### TC-POST-005: 内容为空字符串(应返回400)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/help/publish
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "测试",
  "content": "  ",
  "category": "经验分享",
  "username": "testuser001"
}

### TC-POST-006: 城市字段为字符串"null"
POST http://localhost:8080/api/help/publish
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "测试帖子",
  "content": "测试内容",
  "category": "经验分享",
  "city": "null",
  "username": "testuser001"
}

### 查询帖子列表
GET http://localhost:8080/api/help/list?page=0&size=12

### TC-COMMENT-001: 发表主评论(假设帖子ID为1)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/help/comment
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "postId": 1,
  "content": "很好的帖子",
  "username": "testuser002"
}

### TC-COMMENT-002: 回复某条评论(假设评论ID为1)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/help/comment
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "postId": 1,
  "content": "同意楼上",
  "username": "testuser003",
  "parentId": 1
}

### TC-COMMENT-003: 获取树形评论列表
GET http://localhost:8080/api/help/comments/1

### TC-COMMENT-004: 评论者删除自己的评论
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/help/comment/1?username=testuser002

