DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/help/comment/2?username=testuser003

### TC-COMMENT-006: 删除不存在的评论(应返回400)
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/help/comment/99999?username=testuser001

### TC-POSTDEL-001: 帖子作者删除帖子
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/help/post/1?username=testuser001

