### 注册两个用户用于测试关注
POST http://localhost:8080/api/user/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "user001",
  "password": "123456",
  "realName": "用户1",
  "phone": "13800138020"
}

###
POST http://localhost:8080/api/user/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "user002",
  "password": "123456",
  "realName": "用户2",
  "phone": "13800138021"
}

### TC-FOLLOW-001: 首次关注
POST http://localhost:8080/api/follow/toggle
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "followerUsername": "user001",
  "followingUsername": "user002"
}

### TC-FOLLOW-002: 取消关注
POST http://localhost:8080/api/follow/toggle
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "followerUsername": "user001",
  "followingUsername": "user002"
}

### TC-FOLLOW-003: 关注自己(应返回400)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/follow/toggle
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "followerUsername": "user001",
  "followingUsername": "user001"
}

### TC-FOLLOW-004: 查询粉丝列表
GET http://localhost:8080/api/follow/followers?username=user002&page=0&size=50

### TC-FOLLOW-005: 查询关注数量
GET http://localhost:8080/api/follow/following/count?username=user001

### TC-FOLLOW-006: 关注者不存在(应返回400)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/follow/toggle
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "followerUsername": "nonexistent",
  "followingUsername": "user002"
}

